OL,4,Cintimidation against MPs
OL,6,FThere have always been hugely
OL,7,Fcontroversial issues that have caused
OL,8,Fpeople to get very angry with MPs.
OL,10,FI remember being tasked on one of my
OL,11,Ffirst days working for the Observer
OL,12,Fnewspaper 20 years ago with going
OL,13,Fthrough furious letters from readers
OL,14,Fshocked that the paper had just backed
OL,15,Fthe Iraq War.
OL,17,FAnd if they were that angry with the
OL,18,FObserver, you can imagine how they
OL,19,Ffelt about the Labour politicians and
OL,20,FPM making the decisions.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/18
