OL,4,Cintimidation against MPs
OL,6,FSo, there was abuse. But even then -
OL,7,Fand even over the hugely contentious
OL,8,Fdecision to support the US in the Iraq
OL,9,Fwar - it was nothing like we see now.
OL,11,FThat is why the so-called "mother of
OL,12,Fthe House of Commons" - its longest
OL,13,Fserving woman, Harriet Harman - is now
OL,14,Fcalling for a Speaker's Conference
OL,15,Finto the issue.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/18
