OL,6,FI've watched it evolve over two
OL,7,Fdecades, with key turning points that
OL,8,Fseemed to harden views about MPs,
OL,9,Fperhaps the first big one was the MPs
OL,10,Fexpenses scandal in 2009.
OL,12,FBut even after that, we didn't know
OL,13,Fhow bad it would get.
OL,15,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,16,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,17,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,18,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/18
