OL,6,FI'd known before she decided to become
OL,7,Fan MP as a lovely friend and wonderful
OL,8,Fmother.
OL,10,FI suspect she would never have
OL,11,Fbelieved that among the threats she
OL,12,Fwas walking into with that job was a
OL,13,Fthreat to her life. Surely not for
OL,14,FDavid Amess, either.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/18
