OL,4,Cintimidation against MPs
OL,6,FAnd yet these days MPs are given hefty
OL,7,Fsecurity briefings, with some having
OL,8,Fpanic buttons installed in their
OL,9,Foffices and homes, some advised to
OL,10,Fstop offering open, constituency
OL,11,Fsurgeries, some seeing individuals
OL,12,Fprosecuted for death threats.
OL,14,FIt is clear that has intensified the
OL,15,Fsituation for MPs, and there have been
OL,16,Fsome pretty intimidating moments for a
OL,17,Fnumber of Labour frontbenchers.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/18
