OL,6,FBut talking to MPs it is clear that
OL,7,Fthis isn't about one issue, it is
OL,8,Fabout a bigger societal shift that has
OL,9,Fresulted in hostilities being raised
OL,10,Faround almost every contested issue.
OL,12,FAs Jess Phillips made clear
OL,13,F(describing the levels of Islamophobia
OL,14,Fbeing displayed currently as
OL,15,F"sickening") if there is bullying she
OL,16,Fhas faced, it is no more for this than
OL,17,Ffor many other issues.
OL,19,FI've had MPs tell me that they've
OL,20,Ffaced intense abuse over how they
OL,21,Fvoted on the sewage crisis.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/18
