OL,6,FI know of one who has had to move
OL,7,Ftheir family out of their constituency
OL,8,Fbecause of local anger about the
OL,9,Fpolitical party they belong to.
OL,11,FAnd then there was Brexit.
OL,13,FThat was when I first came across the
OL,14,Fscale of death threats being thrown at
OL,15,FLabour's Diane Abbott, revealing some
OL,16,Fof the messages that were being sent
OL,17,Fto her during that tense period.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/18
