OL,6,FIt was Cox's death that made her
OL,7,Frealise she had to take the
OL,8,Fcorrespondence seriously, as she
OL,9,Frevealed that her staff no longer let
OL,10,Fher walk alone around her constituency.
OL,12,FI asked Labour peer Tom Watson - who
OL,13,Fwas an MP for many years - if he felt
OL,14,Fthere had been a dramatic shift and he
OL,15,Fsaid there was, perhaps intensified by
OL,16,Fthe impact of social media.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/18
