OL,6,FThat allows people to quickly organise
OL,7,Fprotests (now a Facebook post, where
OL,8,F25 years ago, it might have taken
OL,9,Fphone calls and posters) and to exist
OL,10,Fin an echo chamber in which their
OL,11,Fanger can be quickly amplified.
OL,13,FSocial media has brought pile-ons, and
OL,14,Fsometimes violent misinformation.
OL,16,FSpeaking to Watson, he suggested that
OL,17,Fmany MPs would not encourage their
OL,18,Fchildren to follow in their footsteps.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/18
