OL,6,FHarman says that protest that seeks to
OL,7,Fshow strength of opinion and attempts
OL,8,Fto change minds through argument is,
OL,9,Fof course, acceptable. "But trying to
OL,10,Fchange MPs' actions, through fear, is
OL,11,Fnot."
OL,13,FShe also said there was a need to
OL,14,Fdistinguish between the resilience
OL,15,Fexpected from and MP and what is
OL,16,Fexpected from their family - including
OL,17,Fchildren and elderly relatives.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G13/18
