OL,6,FFor Harman this is a "red line" and
OL,7,Fwhy she is so concerned about
OL,8,Fdemonstrations at peoples' homes.
OL,9,FThese happened much less often in the
OL,10,Fpast - but were not unheard of. In
OL,11,Ffact, in 2008 Fathers4Justice scaled
OL,12,Fonto her roof in 2008.
OL,14,FShe also argued that some MPs were
OL,15,Fvulnerable - with mobility
OL,16,Fdisabilities, limited vision, or
OL,17,Fperhaps pregnant - and for them -
OL,18,Fbeing jostled is an additional threat.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G14/18
