OL,6,FAnd she felt it - like Watson - that
OL,7,Fthings were much worse now, partly
OL,8,Fbecause of the targeting of homes,
OL,9,Fpartly because of abuse fuelled via
OL,10,Fsocial media - but perhaps most of
OL,11,Fall, because two colleagues have been
OL,12,Fmurdered, so the threats cannot be
OL,13,Fdismissed.
OL,15,FOne thing many MPs have told me is
OL,16,Fthat the Speaker Lindsay Hoyle is
OL,17,Fgenuinely very passionate and very
OL,18,Ffocused on this issue.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G15/18
