OL,6,FOn the very day that he made the
OL,7,Fdecision to let Labour have an
OL,8,Famendment on the SNP's Israel and Gaza
OL,9,Fmotion, which he accepts was a
OL,10,Fmistake, he had met MPs including the
OL,11,FConservative Tobias Ellwood about this
OL,12,Fissue.
OL,14,FEllwood's home
OL,16,FThe shame in this is that it is a
OL,17,Ftrend that will almost certainly make
OL,18,Fsome people, who might have made very
OL,19,Fgood MPs, choose alternative careers.
